headline: Hershey (HSY): Unpacking Valuation After Shaq Gummy Launch and Conviction List Buzz
summary: Hershey (NYSE:HSY) is catching plenty of attention this week after partnering with Shaquille O'Neal for a nationwide launch of sneaker-shaped gummies. In addition, some upbeat signals from institutional investors are sparking renewed discussion about the company's outlook. See our latest analysis for Hershey. Hershey’s latest headline-grabbing partnership and a boost in institutional sentiment have certainly kept it in the spotlight, but the share price momentum has barely budged this year...
